      <h1 class="heading-primary activity__title">Investitsion loyihalar</h1>
      <h2 class="heading-secondary mb-16">
        O‘zbekiston landshaftlarini barqaror tiklash loyihasi (RESILAND)
        (P174135) buyicha kiskacha malumot:
      </h2>
      <button class="collapsible flex center">
